rows.label: qst400202_msg0001
rows.name: Oh yeah, I heard about that.

rows.label: qst400202_msg0002
rows.name:
Some Superbian dude was saying
they were going to "execute the
prisoner" within the next few days!

rows.label: qst400202_msg0003
rows.name: Those Iira guys are pretty bad, right?

rows.label: qst400202_msg0004
rows.name:
I heard they've killed loads of Drivers
to steal their Core Crystals.

rows.label: qst400202_msg0005
rows.name:
Pretty amazing if the Empire have
really captured one of them!

rows.label: qst400202_msg0006
rows.name:
I wonder what they'll do at this
"execution" thing, anyway.
I've never seen one before!

rows.label: qst400202_msg0008
rows.name:
I've gotta go see for myself!
You guys should come along too!
